				<h3>About Library Management System:</h3>	
				<ul>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;This Library Management System application is developed to provide knowledge to sudents in organizations, and people in the outside world.<br>
					This application is mostly used for Institutions those have libraries. In present days all institutes have libraries. In libraries we have lot of books. And <br>
					present days so many users are using these libraries. We have some problems in present libraries library management have to do much work to <br>maintain library functionalities. 
				</ul>
				<ul>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In this application we have three types of users.
					<li style="margin-left:70px;">Students and Teachers</li>
					<li style="margin-left:70px;">Library Manager</li>
					<li style="margin-left:70px;">Admin user</li>
				</ul>
				<ul>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
					<b>Borrowers:</b> Students can search books, view available of books in library, request for books and get books from the library and return books.
				</ul>
				<ul>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
					<b>Library Manager:</b> Library Manager can see the requested books from the users. View daily status of books In and Out of library. Issue books<br>
					to users and manager can reject users request also. Manager can return books from the users. Manager will enter updates about library, new books added to the library and others.
				</ul>
				<ul>
					&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
					<b>Admin User:</b> Admin users can see the requested books from the users. View total number of books in the library. Admin users can add new books to the libray and they can delete books from the library.
					They can add new users to the library and they can remove users from the library. Admin user can also enter updates about library, new books and other things. 
				</ul>
